commentary: Muzarabani to Mashrafe Mortaza, OUT Another direct hit, another wicket for Zimbabwe. Mushfiq is way short of the crease. So, it takes a pin-point direct hit to end Mushfiq's superbly-controlled knock

commentary: Nasir Hossain to Chigumbura, OUT Nasir has his hands aloft in joy; Bangladesh open the series with a crushing win. Chigumbura is the last man out. Mutumbami out with an injured ankle and will not come out to bat. Flattish and pushed through to ping the pad in front of middle and leg
